iaddrtrace
-----------

Use ptrace to singlestep a program and print the trace of instruction addresses.

Usage
------

    iaddrtrace [options] [--] program [arguments]
    Options:
        -s ADDR     -- Address to start the output in hex
        -d ADDR     -- Address to stop the output in hex
        -o FILE     -- Use FILE instead of stderr

References
-----------
https://blog.tartanllama.xyz/writing-a-linux-debugger-setup/
